.TH MUXM 1 "2025-08-13" "MuxMaster v1.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
muxm \- Universal DV/HLG/HDR10/SDR → MP4 encoder/muxer for Apple TV direct play
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B muxm
[\fIoptions\fR] \fIsource\fR [\fItarget.mp4\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
MuxMaster converts and muxes video to MP4 suitable for Apple TV direct play.
It handles Dolby Vision (extract/convert/inject), HDR/HLG/SDR color handling,
audio selection/transcoding, and subtitle selection with optional PGS→SRT OCR.
.PP
Configuration layers (lowest to highest precedence):
.PP
Defaults → /etc/.muxmrc → ~/.muxmrc → ./.muxmrc → CLI flags
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.BR --dry-run
Plan steps without encoding/muxing (creates placeholders only).
.TP
.BR --output-ext " " EXT
Output container: mp4|m4v|mov. Default: mp4.
.TP
.BR --crf " " N
x265 quality CRF (lower = higher quality). Typical: 18–22.
.TP
.BR -p ", " --preset " " NAME
x265 preset ultrafast..placebo. Default: slower.
.TP
.BR -l ", " --level " " N
x265 level-idc (e.g., 5.1).
.TP
.BR --x265-params " " STR
Advanced x265 parameter string.
.TP
.BR --audio-track " " N
Select specific audio stream index (0-based).
.TP
.BR --audio-lang-pref " " LIST
Preferred audio languages (comma-separated, e.g., eng,spa).
.TP
.BR --stereo-fallback " , " --no-stereo-fallback
Enable/disable automatic AAC stereo track when primary >2ch.
.TP
.BR --sub-lang-pref " " LIST
Preferred subtitle languages (comma-separated).
.TP
.BR --no-ocr
Disable PGS→SRT OCR (PGS will be skipped unless directly mapped).
.TP
.BR --skip-video " , " --skip-audio " , " --skip-subs
Disable respective pipelines (useful for quick tests).
.SH FULL OPTIONS
See \fB--help-all\fR for the comprehensive list, defaults, and notes.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
muxm Movie.mkv out.mp4
muxm --crf 20 -p slow Movie.mkv out.mp4
muxm --audio-lang-pref eng,spa --sub-lang-pref eng --no-ocr Movie.mkv out.mp4
muxm --dry-run --skip-video Movie.mkv out.mp4
.fi
.SH FILES
\fI/etc/.muxmrc\fR, \fI~/.muxmrc\fR, \fI./.muxmrc\fR
.PP
CLI flags always override config files.
